        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>Pottery Neolithic [300263188], Levantine Neolithic periods [300107633], Levantine periods [300107629], Levantine (culture or style) [300019811], Near Eastern (Early Western World) [300019571], Early Western World [300019255], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
